# Example

```js
const image_data = await FileUtility.readFile('./test/assets/PngSuite', 'oi1n0g16', 'png', null);
const image = ImagePNG.fromFile(image_data);
image.decodePixels();
const length = image.pixels.length;
➜ 6144
const pixel = image.getPixel(0, 0);
➜ [255, 255, 255, 255]
```

